quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaaɗi. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollugɗon e moƴƴere, Allah no Anndi ɗum.Yooɓee,ko ɓuri moƴƴude e njooɓa,ko gomɗal. Hulee Lam yo joomiraaɓe haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde ɗaɓɓoton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, Jaŋtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. Jaŋtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muuɗum ko on jeyaaɓe e majjuɓe"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimɓe ɓen yahri ɗon, Insinanoɗon Alla. Pellet Alla ko Yaafotooɗo Huuɓuɗo-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaŋtoree innde Alla wano jaŋtorton baabiraaɓe mo'on, maa ko ɓuri ɗum tiiɗude. No e yimɓe ɓen wi'ooɓe: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara geɓal-moƴƴal"
  2,201,"No e maɓɓe wi'ooɓe: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"Ɓen ɗon, no woodani ɓe geɓal-moƴƴal e kon ko ɓe faggitii. Alla ko Yaawuɗo hasboore"